    <section id="Login">
        <h1>Login</h1>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-9">
                <span class="badge badge-ttl">Method</span>
                <p><pre>void Login()</pre></p>

                <span class="badge badge-ttl">Remark</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>Starts up channel login screen, followed by channel login confirmation and game server login.</li>
                    <li>The progress of channel login, channel login confirmation and game server login is notified via OnLogin.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
