    <section id="LoginCallback">
        <h1>Login Callback</h1>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-9">
                <span class="badge badge-ttl">Method</span>
                <p><pre>void OnLogin(SGUOp action, SGUStateChangeReason reason)</pre></p>

                <span class="badge badge-ttl">Parameters</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>action - one of OP_LOGIN（channel login）, OP_AUTH（channel login confirmation）, OP_LOGINGAME（game server login）</li>
                    <li>reason - one of STATE_CHANGE_REASON_OP（operation ongoing）、STATE_CHANGE_REASON_OP_SUCCESS（operation succeeded）、STATE_CHANGE_REASON_OP_FAILURE（operation failed）、STATE_CHANGE_REASON_OP_CANCELED（operation cancelled）</li>
                </ul>

                <span class="badge badge-ttl">Remark</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>The progress of login is notified to caller via this callback.</li>
                    <li>It's necessary to check both 'action' and 'reason' to judge how far the login flow goes.</li>
                    <li>Failure or cancellation at any stage indicates the failure of whole login flow.</li>
                    <li>Only success of game server login indicates the success of whole login flow, in which case you may unlock appliation functions.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-3">
                <!--<span class="badge badge-ttl">WebView 頁面</span>
                <a href="<%= " assets/img/" + lang + "/pic07.png" %>" data-toggle="lightbox">
                <img src="<%= " assets/img/" + lang + "/pic07.png" %>" class="img-responsive"/>
                </a>-->
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="Logout">
        <h1>Logout</h1>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-9">
                <span class="badge badge-ttl">Method</span>
                <p><pre>void Logout()</pre></p>

                <span class="badge badge-ttl">Remark</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>Start game server logout, followed by channel logout.</li>
                    <li>As long as game server logout succeeded, the whole logout flow is considered as finished regardless of the result of channel logout.</li>
                    <li>The progress of logout is notified via OnLogout.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-3">
                <!--<span class="badge badge-ttl">WebView 頁面</span>
                <a href="<%= " assets/img/" + lang + "/pic07.png" %>" data-toggle="lightbox">
                <img src="<%= " assets/img/" + lang + "/pic07.png" %>" class="img-responsive"/>
                </a>-->
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="LogoutCallback">
        <h1>Logout Callback</h1>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-9">
                <span class="badge badge-ttl">Method</span>
                <p><pre>void OnLogout(SGUStateChangeReason reason)</pre></p>

                <span class="badge badge-ttl">Parameters</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>reason - one of STATE_CHANGE_REASON_OP_SUCCESS（logout success）、STATE_CHANGE_REASON_OP_FAILURE（logout failure）</li>
                </ul>

                <span class="badge badge-ttl">Remark</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>The result of logout flow is notified to caller via this callback.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-3">
                <!--<span class="badge badge-ttl">WebView 頁面</span>
