        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-9">
                <span class="badge badge-ttl">Method</span>
                <p><pre>void Exit(bool silent)</pre></p>

                <span class="badge badge-ttl">Parameters</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>silent - true：do not show confirmation screen，false：show confirmation screen</li>
                </ul>

                <span class="badge badge-ttl">Remark</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>Exit application.</li>
                    <li>You please show your own confirmation screen and call Exit(false) if user selects to exit.</li>
